_sText:
bhop_fosi_unfinished - a pcpie inspired map focused on fun and original gameplay rather than aesthetics

was planning on adding more gameplay to this to make it as lengthy as a typical alvo map, but haven't had much motivation or ideas lately so I thought I'd release it now.

it's fine for playing, the "unfinished" just meant that I planned on adding more when I sent it to a server to playtest.

big thanks to pcpie for giving me help with literally everything in this map, he opened up a whole new way of thinking/creating for me.

optimized run is ~1:45, but nobody will ever get that bc route is stupid and nobody runs long maps anymore
